{{Top|canon=Legal-analyst droid}}
A '''legal analyst droid''', also known as a '''legal droid''' or '''litigation droid'''<ref name="GFT">''[[Galladinium's Fantastic Technology]]''</ref> was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] that could perform governmental functions, including making laws. A terrorist organization on [[Lorrd/Legends|Lorrd]] wanted to replace the government with these droids.

One of these droids was [[HM-3]], who assisted [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] in [[Solo-Niathal coup|removing]] [[Cal Omas]] from power in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]].

